         <abstract>
            <p>
               A short theological treatise. It was probably translated from a Greek Vorlage. It is found in many manuscripts together with other
               Ethiopian theological and liturgical treatises, such as the Ethiopic
               <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2461Testam"/> (as  <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2461Testam#Chapter22">Chapter 22</ref>),
               <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1586Hayman"/>, and <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1544Gebrah"/>.
               Sometimes it is bound together with the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1960Mashaf"/>.</p>
            <p>Not to be confused with the text also known as <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3978Elmastoagya"/>
            </p>
         </abstract>
         
